The '''yorik-akaga''' was a pearlescent picket used by the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. [[Warmaster]] [[Nas Choka]] fielded york-akaga during the final stages of the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]].<ref name="TUF">''[[The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force]]''</ref>

